{"tid":2340300,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"牛丸聖誕餐","createTime":"2020-12-25T10:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T13:05:51.000Z","uid":373442,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9b6de0e2c989f5209ac6a9a161fa82e2a679a5","tid":2340300,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:41:18.000Z","msg":"今日行完山好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身諗住返屋企淥個杯麵就算<br />\n返到屋企附近，見到間越南餐廳啲侍應企哂出門口拉客<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大時大節要好似砵蘭街企街咁都幾慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是就入去幫襯下啦，外賣返到去，我沖埋涼先食都仲好熱，個春卷都仲好脆，蝦餅彈牙，牛丸牛肉檬正常發揮，始終都係堂食好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/darkness.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9m5QE23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9m5QE23.jpg&h=5f4d86d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n祝大家聖誕快樂，希望小店都撐得住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37eeb0c61d19b5b47509f6d6c40e932d474cbb50","tid":2340300,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:41:56.000Z","msg":"點解唔幫襯黃店先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ca0d60afe96bd19dde3f9e7cc4209be3a17926","tid":2340300,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"一個人食咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我啱啱打完羽毛球仲未餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669e0f3041280b3f3c307d726e0f9361f478e869","tid":2340300,"uid":373442,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"37eeb0c61d19b5b47509f6d6c40e932d474cbb50","tid":2340300,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:41:56.000Z","msg":"點解唔幫襯黃店先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:46:22.000Z","msg":"呢間都黃架<